libbc-allocators (1.0.0-1) stable; urgency=medium

  * Initial public release.
  * Pool allocator: general-purpose allocate / reallocate / free
    with a 1 GB default capacity.
  * Arena allocator: bump-pointer with bulk reset, secure-wipe,
    page-release, and string copy helpers.
  * Slab allocator: fixed-size O(1) alloc / free for hot object pools.
  * Context: threads leak-warning callbacks and statistics.
  * Typed array: growable primitive absorbed from bc-containers.
  * Full sanitizer coverage (asan / tsan / ubsan / memcheck) and
    cppcheck-clean sources.

 -- Younes Benmoussa <younes.benmoussa@pm.me>  Sun, 19 Apr 2026 12:00:00 +0000
